Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Hi there! This is Alex from TerraVista Properties. Is this a good time to chat?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Yes, this is a good time. How can I help you?

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Great! I understand you're in the market for a new home. Could you tell me a bit about what you're looking for?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Sure. We're looking for a 3-bedroom house with a yard, and it has to be in a good school district. We also want to stay within our budget of $400,000.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: That sounds like a reasonable request. Have you faced any challenges in your search so far?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Yes, every house we've liked has either been out of our budget or sold before we could make an offer.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: I understand how frustrating that can be. The market is really competitive right now. Have you been working with any other real estate agents?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Weve spoken to a few, but it seems like they just send us generic listings and don't really listen to what we want.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Thats disappointing to hear. At TerraVista Properties, we focus on personalized service. I'll make sure to find listings that specifically match your criteria. How soon are you looking to move?

Speaker: Customer
Text: We were hoping to move within the next three months, but we're flexible if the right house comes along.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Perfect. Ill tailor my search to meet that timeline. Before we proceed, do you have any concerns about working with another real estate company?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Just that we might end up wasting time again. We've already seen so many houses that didn't meet our needs.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: I assure you, we'll avoid those pitfalls. Ill filter out any properties that dont match your requirements and send you only the most relevant options. How does that sound?

Speaker: Customer
Text: That sounds good. What should we do next?

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: I'll start by sending you a few curated listings by the end of the day. Once you review them, we can set up viewings for the ones you like. Does that work for you?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Yes, that works perfectly.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Great! I'll need your email to send the listings. Could you please provide it?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Sure, it's [email@example.com].

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Thank you! Watch for an email from me shortly. If you have any questions or need anything else, feel free to call or email me anytime.

Speaker: Customer
Text: Will do. Thanks a lot for your help.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: My pleasure. Speak to you soon!

Speaker: Customer
Text: Bye.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Goodbye!
